      <title>印度重申季风降雨充沛，有利于农作物生长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/india-reiterates-ample-monsoon-rain-forecast-in-boost-to-crops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度维持对高于正常水平的季风的预测，这提振了该国近一半农田的主要灌溉来源是水稻、大豆和棉花等作物的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/india-reiterates-ample-monsoon-rain-forecast-in-boost-to-crops</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 12:01:42 GMT</pubDate>
